java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, javax.swing.WindowConstants
public class Create
extends javax.swing.JFrame

This is a module that allows someone to create a test. It allows you to set the type of question and the worth of the question. A help module is included to show the user how to format each type of question so that the program knows how to interpret them and display them correctly to a student.
